    public class TrackerMapActivity
extends android.support.v7.app.AppCompatActivity
implements com.google.android.gms.maps.OnMapReadyCallback, android.support.v4.app.ActivityCompat.OnRequestPermissionsResultCallback, VehicleChangeListener, BusStopListener
    This is the central activity of the project which displays the bus locations on the Google Maps and It has the option of showing bus stops and bus stop schedule on the Map.
    Data Structure :
    We have used ArrayList in the class to store the list of vehicles, bus stops. We have used HashMap to Map the bus name to the list of schedule.
    Created by Anurag Chitnis on 10/5/2016.
